@page "/About"
@layout MainLayout

<MudContainer>
    <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">
        This application was developed by <MudLink Href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/palvarezrio" Typo="Typo.h6">Pablo Alvarez</MudLink>
        as a basic proof of concept of a web based asset management tool. Using only open source tools clients can be provided with a solution 
        to help them manage a collection of assets and updating information without the need of special knowledge of tools.
